						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa, Parakēsarivarman, Year 4 = c. 11th Century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This is much damaged. It records a gift of gold for burning a perpetual lamp in the Kudal-Āḻvār shrine by the queen of Mummuḍichōḻa-Perumāḷ, whose name cannot be properly made out.</p>						

